Type: Package
Package: purpleAirAPI
Title: Historical Data Retrieval from PurpleAir Sensors via API
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Heba Abdelrazzak <hebaarazzak@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Heba Abdelrazzak <hebaarazzak@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides functions to retrieve historical data
    and sensor metadata from the PurpleAir API.  It allows users to
    download data in chunks to manage API limitations and includes
    functions for accessing sensor location and creation metadata.
